&lt;p&gt;Are you a Prescriber looking for an exciting new opportunity?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bramingham Park Medical Centre are looking for 16 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be an autonomous practitioner working independently and in conjunction with other health care professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Minor injury and illness qualification essential and the ability to maintain and monitor high standards of care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is staff parking available onsite and a large supermarket and several other shops close by.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information please contact recruitment@operosehealth.co.uk&lt;/p&gt;
